ps%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fuae-lottery-revises-payouts-dh30m-and-dh5m-prizes-now-split-among-winners%2Famp_articleshow%2F125786780.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fuae-lottery-revises-payouts-dh30m-and-dh5m-prizes-now-split-among-winners%2Famp_articleshow%2F125786780.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Netflix%20to%20acquire%20Warner%20Bros.%20for%20%2472%20billion%20in%20a%20deal%20that%20could%20reshape%20Hollywood%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Netflix.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68dd5f425dbc4fd10da9f712%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20urged%20his%20X%20followers%20to%20cancel%20their%20Netflix%20subscriptions%20on%20Wednesday.%3Cp%3EIllustration%20by%20Sheldon%20Cooper%2FSOPA%20Images%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENetflix%20is%20buying%20Warner%20Bros.%2C%20adding%20HBO%20and%20major%20franchises%20like%20%26quot%3BHarry%20Potter%26quot%3B%20to%20its%20content%20slate.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENetflix%20said%20the%20deal%20has%20an%20equity%20value%20of%20%2472%20billion%2C%20its%20biggest%20ever%20acquisition.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20deal%20boosts%20Netflix's%20studio%20power%2C%20expanding%20its%20production%20capacity%20and%20theatrical%20output.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20is%20taking%20a%20massive%20swing%20at%20the%20future%20of%20entertainment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20streaming%20giant%20is%20making%20the%20biggest%20acquisition%20in%20its%20history%20%E2%80%94%20and%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20ever%20in%20entertainment%20%E2%80%94%20announcing%20Friday%20that%20it%20has%20struck%20a%20deal%20to%20acquire%20Warner%20Bros.%20from%20Warner%20Bros.%20Discovery%20(WBD)%20for%20an%20equity%20value%20of%20%2472%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cash-and-stock%20deal%2C%20which%20has%20a%20total%20enterprise%20value%20of%20%2482.7%20billion%2C%20will%20bring%20together%20Netflix's%20streaming%20platform%20with%20Warner%20Bros.'%20century-old%20studio%2C%20HBO%2C%20HBO%20Max%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20most%20iconic%20franchises%20in%20film%20and%20television.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20acquisition%20is%20expected%20to%20close%20after%20WBD%20spins%20off%20its%20Global%20Networks%20division%20into%20a%20separate%20publicly%20traded%20company%2C%20Discovery%20Global%2C%20a%20process%20expected%20to%20happen%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a9208709-41d6-45aa-987d-e4745f5eb61f%5C%22%3E'Our%20mission%20has%20always%20been%20to%20entertain%20the%20world'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20co-CEO%20Ted%20Sarandos%20said%20the%20merger%20strengthens%20the%20company's%20core%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20called%20Warner%20Bros.'%20catalog%20%26quot%3Bincredible%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20that%20bringing%20together%20classics%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BCitizen%20Kane%26quot%3B%20with%20Netflix%20hits%20like%20%26quot%3BStranger%20Things%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BKPop%20Demon%20Hunters%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%26quot%3B%20will%20allow%20the%20company%20to%20entertain%20the%20world%20%26quot%3Beven%20better.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESarandos%20said%20this%20merger%20will%20let%20Netflix%20give%20audiences%20%26quot%3Bmore%20of%20what%20they%20love%26quot%3B%20while%20helping%20shape%20the%20next%20century%20of%20global%20storytelling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20plans%20to%20preserve%20Warner%20Bros.'%20existing%20operations%2C%20including%20its%20theatrical%20release%20pipeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223c4d278f-9d1a-45d4-a6bb-0075ba8cee50%5C%22%3EWhy%20Netflix%20wants%20this%20deal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWarner%20Bros.%20grants%20Netflix%20access%20to%20some%20of%20the%20most%20recognizable%20titles%20in%20modern%20entertainment%2C%20including%20enduring%20sitcoms%20like%20%26quot%3BFriends%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Big%20Bang%20Theory%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20well%20as%20prestige%20television%20from%20HBO%2C%20franchises%20like%20%26quot%3BHarry%20Potter%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20classic%20movies%20like%20%26quot%3BThe%20Wizard%20of%20Oz%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BCasablanca.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20also%20significantly%20expands%20Netflix's%20production%20capabilities%20in%20the%20US%20and%20establishes%20the%20company%20as%20a%20more%20powerful%20theatrical%20pipeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Netflix%20built%20its%20empire%20on%20original%20programming%2C%20it%20has%20long%20lacked%20the%20kind%20of%20heritage%20intellectual%20property%20that%20more%20established%20studios%2C%20such%20as%20Disney%2C%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20regulators%20approve%20the%20deal%2C%20Netflix%20subscribers%20are%20likely%20to%20get%20a%20much%20wider%20selection%20of%20premium%20content%20on%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20expects%20the%20acquisition%20to%20deliver%20%242-3%20billion%20in%20annual%20cost%20savings%20by%20the%20third%20year%20and%20to%20boost%20earnings%20by%20the%20second%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWBD%20shareholders%20will%20receive%20%2423.25%20in%20cash%20per%20share%20and%20%244.501%20in%20Netflix%20stock%2C%20Netflix%20said.%20The%20agreement%20values%20WBD%20at%20%2427.75%20per%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20acquisition%20closes%2C%20WBD%20will%20spin%20off%20Discovery%20Global%20%E2%80%94%20a%20company%20that%20will%20house%20CNN%2C%20TNT%20Sports%2C%20Discovery%20Channel%2C%20Discovery%2B%2C%20and%20Bleacher%20Report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegulators%20are%20expected%20to%20scrutinize%20the%20deal%20closely.%20It%20still%20requires%20approval%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%2C%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%2C%20and%20WBD%20shareholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww