e%20I%20had%20lots%20of%20passion%20but%20little%20ability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20with%20her%20father%20at%20her%20graduation.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6932d0737ecd1d1da662fd3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPainting%20makes%20the%20author%20feel%20closer%20to%20her%20father.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Tayla%20Blaire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e5a6e38c-aaa5-4c03-9b83-7dac80a46212%5C%22%3ESomething%20shifted%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20art%2C%20too%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20desire%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhobbies-crafts%2Fbest-art-supplies%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elearn%20about%20art%3C%2Fa%3E%20started%20with%20hoarding%20my%20dad's%20paintings.%20He%20had%20a%20stack%20of%20hundreds%20of%20them.%20My%20mom%20and%20I%20sat%20together%2C%20choosing%20our%20favorites%20to%20frame%20in%20our%20homes.%20I%20chose%20his%20painting%20of%20Eilean%20Donan%20in%20Scotland%20and%20the%20Colosseum%20in%20Rome%2C%20two%20places%20I%20loved%20visiting.%20I%20also%20chose%20a%20beachscape%20with%20two%20silhouette%20figures%20that%20reminded%20me%20of%20my%20dad%20and%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sat%20and%20stared%20at%20them%20for%20months.%20Each%20painting%20was%20a%20slice%20of%20time%20from%20my%20dad's%20life.%20His%20hands%20held%20each%20page.%20His%20brushstrokes%20made%20each%20mark.%20His%20eyes%20chose%20each%20color.%20I've%20always%20kept%20a%20mental%20list%20of%20the%20things%20that%20need%20to%20be%20snatched%20from%20my%20home%20if%20there's%20a%20fire.%20Dad's%20paintings%20are%20now%20top%20of%20that%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20months%20ago%2C%20I%20saw%20an%20ad%20for%20a%20watercolor%20painting%20workshop%20near%20me.%20'Beginners%20Welcome.'%20I%20went%20alone%20and%20spent%20three%20hours%20painting%20a%20dahlia.%20I%20found%20another%20workshop%20across%20town%20a%20few%20weeks%20later%20and%20painted%20a%20Tuscan%20house%20among%20poppies.%20I%20then%20found%20a%20two-day%20oil%20painting%20workshop%20and%20went%20to%20that%2C%20too%2C%20enjoying%20the%20challenge%20of%20a%20different%20medium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225598%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20watercolor%20is%20on%20the%20left%2C%20her%20father's%20is%20on%20the%20right.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6930585404d0f0a114f150d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223682%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20watercolor%20is%20on%20the%20left%2C%20and%20one%20of%20her%20father's%20is%20on%20the%20right.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Tayla%20Blaire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225c234c6c-f1ab-4e27-8e1e-1fa5eee54c92%5C%22%3EMy%20new%20hobby%20has%20helped%20me%20feel%20more%20connected%20to%20my%20dad%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUsually%2C%20when%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-shares-joy-taking-a-new-hobby-alongside-her-kids-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epick%20up%20a%20hobby%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20demand%20immediate%20excellence%20or%20abandon%20it.%20Painting%20is%20different.%20I'm%20learning%20slowly.%20I'm%20using%20the%20expertise%20of%20others%2C%20in%20person%20where%20possible%20and%20online%20when%20not.%20I'm%20making%20mistakes%2C%20but%20I'm%20making%20them%20holding%20my%20dad's%20brushes%20(the%20salvageable%20ones%20%E2%80%94%20he%20wasn't%20particularly%20diligent%20when%20it%20came%20to%20washing%20them).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20read%20that%20losing%20a%20parent%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-deal-with-homesickness-loneliness-living-abroad-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esense%20of%20homesickness%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20never%20goes%20away.%20It's%20the%20best%20description%20of%20grief%20that%20I've%20found.%20Picking%20up%20my%20dad's%20hobby%20creates%20a%20tiny%20tether%20to%20him.%20It%20doesn't%20remove%20the%20homesickness.%20It%20doesn't%20ease%20the%20grief%20%E2%80%94%20if%20anything%2C%20it%20agitates%20it%2C%20swirling%20it%20around%20like%20cleaning%20a%20paintbrush%20in%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20sometimes%20that's%20exactly%20what%20I%20want.%20I%20want%20to%20sit%20in%20the%20grief.%20I%20hold%20his%20brushes%2C%20I%20listen%20to%20his%20playlist%2C%20and%20I%20do%20the%20thing%20he%20loved%20doing%2C%20aware%20that%20I'll%20never%20have%20the%20privilege%20of%20doing%20it%20beside%20him.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20his%20hand%20guides%20mine.%20Together%2C%20we%20make%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdad-died-grief-connect-painting-hobby-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1764936781000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6931a40404d0f0a114f165c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdad-died-grief-connect-painting-hobby-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20dad%20died%20last%20year%2C%20and%20it%20still%20makes%20no%20sense%20to%20me.%20I've%20picked%20up%20his%20painting%20hobby%2C%20and%20it's%20created%20a%20tiny%20tether%20to%20feel%20connected%20to%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Tayla%20Blaire)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdad-died-grief-connect-painting-hobby-2025-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20Orders%20High-Level%20Probe%20Into%20IndiGo%20Crisis%2C%20Expects%20Fix%20In%203%20Days%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22In%20what%20will%20be%20music%20to%20the%20ears%20of%20passengers%20hit%20hard%20by%20the%20IndiGo%20disruptions%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20said%20flight%20schedules%20are%20expected%20to%20stabilise%20b