ound%20elephants%20would%20testify%20that%20the%20two%20share%20a%20bond.%20He%20understands%20them.%20And%20the%20relationship%20is%20reciprocal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubstantial%20proof%20of%20his%20love%20for%20the%20wild%20lies%20in%20the%20five%20organisations%20that%20he%20has%20created%20%E2%80%94%20TRAFFIC%20India%20%E2%80%94%20a%20wildlife%20trade%20monitoring%20network%3B%20NGO%20Srishti%20%E2%80%94%20an%20organisation%20founded%20to%20protect%20the%20environment%20in%20Delhi%3B%20Delhi%20Bird%20Club%3B%20Venu%20Menon%20Animal%20Allies%20Foundation%3B%20and%20Wildlife%20Trust%20of%20India%20(WTI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation_11zon-1723468141.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20wild%20elephant%20herd%20in%20Keonjhar%2C%20Odisha%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation_11zon-1723468141.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation_11zon-1723468141-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation_11zon-1723468141-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation_11zon-1723468141-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation_11zon-1723468141-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360931%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20wild%20elephant%20herd%20in%20Keonjhar%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vivek%20Menon%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPicture%20a%20world%20where%20trade%20in%20wild%20plants%20and%20animals%20is%20managed%20at%20sustainable%20levels%20without%20damaging%20the%20integrity%20of%20ecological%20systems.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20TRAFFIC%20India%20has%20attempted%20to%20do%20since%20the%20outset.%20Menon%20who%20co-founded%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F48373%2Fwildlife-trade-trafficking-india-humane-society%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildlife%20trade%20monitoring%20%3C%2Fa%3Enetwork%20with%20his%20colleague%20and%20legendary%20conservationist%20Ashok%20Kumar%2C%20emphasises%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20resolve%20to%20bust%20poaching%20amid%20other%20illegal%20activities.%20The%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20work%20also%20extends%20to%20the%20fight%20against%20illegal%20international%20ivory%20trade.%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20work%20earned%20him%20the%20RG%20Samsara%20Lifetime%20Achievement%20Award%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20activism%20is%20important%2C%20this%20biologist%20believes%20in%20shedding%20an%20equal%20spotlight%20on%20creating%20impact%20through%20policy%20frameworks.%20As%20Chair%20of%20the%20Asian%20Elephant%20Specialist%20Group%20for%20the%20IUCN%20(International%20Union%20for%20Conservation%20of%20Nature)%20for%20the%20past%2012%20years%2C%20Menon%20elaborates%20on%20the%20nature%20of%20his%20work%20in%20advising%20various%20governments%20on%20%E2%80%9Cdoing%20things%20right%20for%20elephants%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20includes%20bringing%20out%20scientific%20work%2C%20guidelines%2C%20and%20manuals.%20It%20also%20includes%20planning%20linear%20infrastructure%3B%20highways%2C%20railways%2C%20road%20passes%2C%20and%20power%20lines%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20the%20elephants%20are%20allowed%20to%20pass%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20segues%20into%20the%20topic%20of%20identifying%20and%20protecting%20elephant%20corridors%2C%20a%20brainchild%20of%20the%20Wildlife%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20overarching%20goal%20being%20to%20secure%20a%20%E2%80%98rite%20of%20passage%E2%80%99%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F188598%2Felephant-doctor-assam-treats-hundreds-wildlife-hero-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebig%20mammals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20WTI%20along%20with%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20top%20scientists%20have%20identified%20and%20surveyed%20101%20such%20functional%20corridors%20across%2011%20states%20for%20the%2029%2C000%20odd%20Asian%20Elephants%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20a%20spare%20bedroom%20project%20to%20a%20phenomenal%20trust%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%202023%20study%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EJournal%20of%20Wildlife%20and%20Biodiversity%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20corridors%20are%20short%20strips%20of%20forests%20that%20link%20two%20larger%20parts%20of%20the%20forest%3B%20like%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccontinuous%20two-dimensional%20landscape%20structure%20that%20interconnects%20two%20or%20more%20previously%20linked%20areas%20of%20animal%20habitats%E2%80%9D.%20These%20enable%20the%20animals%20to%20disperse%2C%20reduce%20their%20risk%20of%20separation%20and%20make%20habitat%20rehabilitation%20easier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20explored%20how%20anthropogenic%20stress%2C%20the%20development%20of%20roads%20and%20railways%2C%20and%20hydroelectric%20projects%20are%20hampering%20these%20corridors.%20The%20problem%20is%20compounded%20by%20multiple%20forests%20being%20turned%20into%20croplands%20by%20the%20farming%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Ta